column5: My first one, still very dark (both the fish and the light), that's my blood btw:   One of my brother's from later in the morning:   Another one of my brother's:   I got get my brother a digital camera. He landed 5 or 6 all on roe. I landed 2, both on plugs. We seemed to do better than most, but maybe that's just me.  Headed home by 8:30am.
A Wiggle Wart!  Very nice feesh.
Wow! your Brothers look alot alike!
Great looking fish, congrats. Nice way to kick off the year.  Mike
Great report and pics!!!  Human blood and a spinning reel with a Steelhead!!!... it don't get no better than that!!!
Great fish.  Clearly you earned them with all that blood being spilled.  Nice job.
